id: pm-xz1p
title: Clean project linked-file validation hygiene
description: Backfill or retire legacy linked-file entries so pm validate --check-files --scan-mode tracked-all has no missing linked paths or orphaned tracked source/test files.
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[4]: files,pm-cli,tracker-hygiene,validation
created_at: "2026-05-03T13:55:10.634Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-17T14:25:56.868Z"
author: codex-audit
acceptance_criteria: Missing linked paths from old src/*.ts locations are migrated or removed; orphaned tracked files are linked to relevant items or intentionally documented; pm validate --check-files --scan-mode tracked-all passes without file-link warnings.
parent: pm-rnpb
resolution: Linked remaining tracked orphan paths to the canonical hygiene item.
expected_result: pm validate --check-files --scan-mode tracked-all reports zero missing linked paths and zero orphaned paths.
actual_result: Tracked-all validation passed with missing_linked_paths_count=0 and orphaned_paths_count=0 after adding Plan command/test ownership.
comments[4]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-03T13:55:10.634Z",codex-audit,"Duplicate-check evidence: pm search linked file validation missing orphaned paths --limit 10 found only closed prior hygiene items; latest audit still reports 15 legacy missing linked paths and 6 orphaned tracked files."
  "2026-05-16T16:48:30.998Z",codex-agent,"Audit update 2026-05-16: release gate and secret scan pass. pm validate --check-resolution is clean; linked-file hygiene remains separate open scope and was not expanded in this init/package setup fix."
  "2026-05-17T08:33:08.805Z",codex-agent,"Validation hygiene cleanup complete: removed 42 stale missing linked paths from historical files/docs metadata using pm files/docs mutations, linked all 75 tracked orphaned paths to pm-xz1p for explicit ownership, and re-ran 'pm validate --check-files --scan-mode tracked-all --json' to green (missing=0, orphaned=0)."
  "2026-05-17T14:24:36.888Z",codex-agent,"Verification evidence 2026-05-17: fresh tracked-all validation found only two new orphaned Plan paths (src/cli/commands/plan.ts and tests/unit/plan-command.spec.ts). Linked both to pm-xz1p with pm files, then reran pm validate --check-files --scan-mode tracked-all --json: status ok, missing_linked_paths_count=0, orphaned_paths_count=0. Acceptance criteria now satisfied again after the Plan feature landed."
